  <h3>Knowledge Profile and Rationale</h3>
  <p class="justify">
    The project depends on software design knowledge, mobile application development, cloud backend integration, and algorithmic reasoning. A change in
    one module, such as user profile structure, directly affects UI rendering, repository logic, backend rules, and test behavior. This interdependence is
    a defining feature of complex problem solving.
  </p>

